prompt:
SCENE: Achievement/trophy visualization.
- Center: A glowing trophy or badge
  - Trophy design: Modern, geometric, not traditional
  - Text area left blank for overlay
- Background: Particle effects like confetti or sparkles
- Around trophy: Small icons representing the concepts:
  - Small arrow (morphism)
  - Small box (functor)
  - Small combined orbs (monoid)
  - Small nested-then-flat boxes (monad)
- Celebratory but not cheesy

STYLE:
- Achievement unlocked aesthetic
- Neon glow
- Dark background with celebration particles

CONSTRAINTS:
- No text (achievement text will be overlaid)
- No characters
- Family-friendly
- Original artwork only
